media:group.media:title: She-Hulk - It's A "Comedy"
media:group.media:description: Since we're just a day or two out from the release of She-Hulk Attorney At Law, which I'm sure will be a hilariously entertaining legal comedy, I thought I'd take a look at some of the clips that have been released so far, so we can all bask in the glow of comedy gold.
